# debian/conffiles — user-editable configuration files
#
# dpkg will preserve these files across upgrades (rather than overwriting them)
# and warn the user if the package provides a newer version that differs from
# what is installed.
#
# The .env file for the vendored tt-inference-server contains site-specific
# secrets (JWT_SECRET, AUTHORIZATION_TOKEN, model cache paths) and must
# survive package upgrades without being clobbered.
